ComicInfo.Summary: Void investigates the going-ons in the planet of Khera and searches for Voodoo. Every person she asks has no idea where Voodoo could be, believing that she was probably in some bar or dancing somewhere. When she asked Spartan, he informed her that she was probably in the isolated area underground. Void checked to find Voodoo there in a kind of slum area where other Daemonites where. Voodoo informs Void that the war between the Kherubium and the Daemonites has been over for 300 years, but no one knew about it. Meanwhile, on Earth, Savant's WildC.A.T.s attack H.A.R.M. of Troika, believing he is the brains of the trio. Condition Red shoots H.A.R.M., killing him.
